          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>Tenderstem</strong> <strong>broccoli</strong> to a pot with a matching lid with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cover with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for an initial 2-3 min or until almost cooked</p><p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong> then shake off any excess water</p>",
